JEDDAH: Prince Badr bin Sultan, deputy governor of the Makkah region, received on Monday in the governorate headquarters in Jeddah Ayman Abo Abah, acting CEO of Jeddah Airports Co. Prince Badr was briefed on the preparations at King Abdulaziz International Airport for the Hajj season, including the measures implemented to ensure the safety of departing pilgrims after they had performed Hajj rituals. 